<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

<main>
  <div class="about-top section-bloop">

  <section class="page-hero page-hero-short">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Our Story</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about-origin">
    <div class="container grid-2 gap-xl">
      <div class="about-img-block">
        <div class="about-img-frame">
          <div class="about-logo-large"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-img-caption">Est. 2026 — Pretoria, South Africa</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">How It Started</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">From a weekend market<br/><em>to something more.</em></h2>
        <p>Con Leche grew out of weekend market pop-ups in Pretoria. The founder is a cat person and a coffee person, and wanted a space that felt like neither a chain nor a lecture. Just a good cup, made properly, in a place worth sitting in.</p>
        <p>The name is straightforward. <em>Con leche</em> means with milk. It's coffee made the way you like it, not the way someone thinks you should.</p>
        <p>The truck came after the markets. The regulars came after the truck. Now it's a Saturday ritual for a lot of people, and we take that seriously.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  </div><!-- /about-top -->

  <section class="section section-cream about-mission">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">What we're about</p>
      <h2 class="section-title text-center">Four things that<br/><em>matter to us.</em></h2>
      <div class="values-grid">

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-card-img">
            <!-- Replace src with a real photo when ready -->
            <div class="value-card-placeholder"></div>
            <div class="value-card-fade"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card-body">
            <h3>The Cat Thing</h3>
            <p>Our spaces are cat-friendly. Sometimes the cats show up uninvited — that's fine with us. We work with local shelters and put some of what we earn back into cat welfare in the area.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-card-img">
            <div class="value-card-placeholder"></div>
            <div class="value-card-fade"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card-body">
            <h3>Community First</h3>
            <p>Run clubs, painting evenings, market days. These aren't marketing. They're what we actually want to be doing. Coffee is the reason people show up. Community is the reason they come back.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-card-img">
            <div class="value-card-placeholder"></div>
            <div class="value-card-fade"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card-body">
            <h3>Made Properly</h3>
            <p>Single-origin beans, decent extraction, baristas who know what they're doing. Pastries baked fresh each morning. If it's not good enough it doesn't go out. Simple as that.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-card-img">
            <div class="value-card-placeholder"></div>
            <div class="value-card-fade"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card-body">
            <h3>We Come to You</h3>
            <p>The truck goes where people are. Markets, corporate parks, running trails. Good coffee shouldn't be hard to find. We try to be where you already are.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about-cta">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Ready to start<br/><em>collecting?</em></h2>
      <p>Create your account and every drink counts toward something.</p>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get your QR code →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
